\b Is it possible to import MIDI files as Calliope documents?
\b0 \
\
I have been investigating the translation of MIDI files, but am sufficiently perplexed to postpone implementation for the moment.  MIDI does not provide much of the typographical information required to set up a score.  Yet, I notice advertisements about programs claiming to convert MIDI to scores.  I just do not understand how such claims can be justified.  I suspect there are some hidden conventions about channels relating to staves etc.  If anybody is in a position to advise me on this, please contact me.\

